      "content": "i feel like im just stuck in this same shitty cycle over and over again. i try to fix things, like get a better job or stay clean or whatever, but it always just falls apart and i end up right back at zero. it’s like i’m just a broken machine that keeps breaking. i don't think it's ever gonna change.",
