    "summary": "The user expresses profound hopelessness and suicidal ideation, describing life as an inescapable, exhausting cycle and suggesting that \"breaking it permanently\" is the only exit. The assistant responds with empathetic reframing and attempts to provide coping strategies/small steps, maintaining a stance of supportive encouragement for life.",
